igh transparency<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-audit-counting-method\">Audit Counting Method<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-audit-counting-method\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-audit-counting-method\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Hand count\/review only<\/option><option value=\"2\">Mix of machine and hand count<\/option><option value=\"3\">Counting method determined by election officials<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-type-of-audit-units\">Type of Audit Units<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-type-of-audit-units\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-type-of-audit-units\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Precincts\/districts<\/option><option value=\"2\">Machines<\/option><option value=\"4\">Individual ballots<\/option><option value=\"5\">Mix of types<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-contests-and-issues-audited\">Contests and Issues Audited<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-contests-and-issues-audited\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-contests-and-issues-audited\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Every contest and ballot issue on the ballot is audited<\/option><option value=\"2\">Pre-specified statewide contests are audited, but no other contests<\/option><option value=\"3\">All statewide contests are eligible to be audited, but no other contests<\/option><option value=\"4\">Both some statewide and some other contests are audited<\/option><option value=\"5\">Statute does not specify contests\/issues audited<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-addressing-discrepancies\">Addressing Discrepancies<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-addressing-discrepancies\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-addressing-discrepancies\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Statute specifies criteria to expand the audit (less than statewide)<\/option><option value=\"2\">Statute specifies criteria to expand the audit (up to statewide)<\/option><option value=\"3\">Statute specifies use of a risk-limiting audit<\/option><option value=\"4\">No statutory guidance for expanding the audit<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-timeline\">Timeline<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-timeline\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-timeline\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Audit completed before results are finalized<\/option><option value=\"2\">Audit completed after results are finalized<\/option><option value=\"3\">Statute does not specify when audit is completed<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n\t<label for=\"wpv-wpcf-binding-on-official-outcomes\">Binding on Official Outcomes<\/label>\n\t<select id=\"wpv_control_select_wpcf-binding-on-official-outcomes\" name=\"wpv-wpcf-binding-on-official-outcomes\" class=\"js-wpv-filter-trigger form-control\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">Select Option<\/option><option value=\"1\">Audit results binding upon official outcomes<\/option><option value=\"2\">Audits normally can alter totals but not outcomes<\/option><option value=\"3\">Results are not binding on official outcomes<\/option><option value=\"4\">No statutory guidance whether audit results are binding<\/option><\/select>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"buttons-wrapper\">\n<input type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-submit wpv-submit-trigger js-wpv-submit-trigger btn\" name=\"wpv_filter_submit\" value=\"Submit\" \/>\n<input type=\"button\" cl