 public reporting<\/em><\/li>\n<li><strong>High transparency:<\/strong> <em>public observation; public reporting; observers can verify marks on ballots<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; el_class=&#8221;support-banner&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class=&#8221;banner-title&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"title-label\">Support<\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"red-text\">Secure<\/span> <span class=\"blue-text\">Elections<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner gap=&#8221;30&#8243;][vc_column_inner el_class=&#8221;right-border&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 class=\"red-text\">Donate to Verified Voting<\/h4>\n<p>A strong and healthy democracy depends on the security of our elections. Join us and help ensure that every vote counts.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"donate-link\" href=\"\/donate\/\">Donate<\/a>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h4 class=\"blue-text\">Join Our Mailing List<\/h4>\n<p>The election landscape is constantly changing and full of complexities. We\u2019ll keep you informed on what\u2019s happening, and what we\u2019re doing to make elections accurate and secure.<\/p>\n<div class=\"wpcf7 no-js\" id=\"wpcf7-f180-o1\" lang=\"en-US\" dir=\"ltr\" data-wpcf7-id=\"180\">\n<div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"true\"><\/p> <ul><\/ul><\/div>\n<form action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/5420#wpcf7-f180-o1\" method=\"post\" class=\"wpcf7-form init mailchimp-ext-0.5.72\" aria-label=\"Contact form\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" data-status=\"init\">\n<div style=\"display: none;\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7\" value=\"180\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_version\" value=\"6.0\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" value=\"en_US\" \/>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_wpcf7_unit_tag\" value=\"wpcf7-f180-o1\" \/>\n